/* ============================================================================
 * STMC_COST_CODES — generated from STMC_COST_CODES_FOR_QUICKBOOKS_API_INTEGRATION.xlsm
 * 
 * Single source of truth for cost code → QuickBooks account mapping.
 * Every budget line in the wizard tags itself with btCode + qbAccount at write
 * time, so the Django backend can POST directly to QuickBooks Online without
 * needing to do its own lookup.
 * 
 * QB INTEGRATION TARGET ENTITY:
 *   For STMC's flow (contractor sends invoice, STMC pays later from QB):
 *   use QB's `Bill` entity, NOT `Purchase`. Bill creates an AP record;
 *   Purchase records an immediate cash/check disbursement.
 *   
 *   Endpoint: POST /v3/company/{realmId}/bill
 *   Each budget line becomes a Bill.Line with:
 *     - DetailType: 'AccountBasedExpenseLineDetail'
 *     - AccountRef.name = the qbAccount value below
 *     - ClassRef.name = the project's class (Branch:Project)
 *     - Amount = line.amount
 *     - Description = line.description
 * 
 * REGENERATION:
 *   This file is generated from the workbook. To regenerate, edit the workbook,
 *   re-run the extraction script, and replace this file.
 * ============================================================================ */

